NME</em>的Rhian Daly的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/wet-leg-wet-leg-review-radar-3196323">发光五星级评论</a>，他写道：“湿腿开始生活，而Teasdale和Chambers则在节日期间骑了摩天轮，两人决定给音乐给音乐另一个机会；合适的是，他们的首张专辑感觉就像是一场围绕Funfair的头晕竞赛，那些讨厌的低谷以机智和智慧的斗争，就像一场口头whack-a-mole的游戏一样。”</p><p> Wet Leg的“ Angelica”被<em>NME</em>冠冕为<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/the-50-best-songs-of-2022-3358809">2022年第13首最好的歌曲</a>，他们在<em>NME</em>列出了<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/the-50-best-albums-of-2022-3363070">2022年的50张最佳专辑</a>中的第二名，安德鲁·斯泰勒尔（Andrew Strendell和班级发行的一张专辑不仅辜负了炒作，而且在英国吉他音乐的脸上拍了一个急需的微笑。”</p><p>在其他地方，湿腿将在少数节日中表演，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2025-line-up-announced-headliners-tickets-3843426">格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kneecap-wet-leg-underworld-tv-on-the-radio-announced-for-green-man-2025-3841849">绿人（Green Man）</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-blink-182-and-deftones-lead-stacked-shaky-knees-2025-line-up-3841297">摇摇欲坠的膝盖Festiva</a> L， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nine-inch-nails-doechii-lola-young-more-join-stacked-roskilde-2025-3832591">Roskilde Festival</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wilderness-2025-festival-line-up-announced-with-basement-jaxx-supergrass-wet-leg-aurora-air-and-more-buy-tickets-3832579">Wilderness Festival</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bbc-radio-1-big-weekend-2025-sam-fender-wet-leg-myles-smith-and-blossoms-lead-line-up-3832459">BBC Radio 1</a>在Liverpool， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/50-cent-biffy-clyro-and-snow-patrol-head-eye-catching-trnsmt-2025-festival-line-up-tickets-3818465">TRNSMT 2025</a> ，BOOLDMASTERS， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-the-prodigy-london-grammar-nelly-furtado-lead-boardmasters-2025-line-up-3816511">BOOLD Masters</a> ，现在， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-bicep-cmat-wet-leg-english-teacher-lead-stacked-line-up-for-irelands-all-together-now-2025-3814778">所有人在一起，现在</a>是ØyaFestival， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-khruangbin-wet-leg-mj-lenderman-among-first-names-for-oya-2025-line-up-3813941">ØyaFestival。</a></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wet-leg-announce-their-return-were-so-back-3846997">潮湿的腿宣布他们的回报：“我们回来了”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
